From ba8af83729252a53a981e272313e8776e3df8caa Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matteo Papadopoulos <spleenteo@hey.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 12:41:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] perf(fot): surgical revalidation, 60d ISR TTL, lean cards,
 paginate /libri, remove llms-full

Cut Vercel Fast Origin Transfer (Hobby 10 GB cap; multimage-astro was 96.4% of ~7.5 GB).

1. Surgical revalidation: /api/revalidate parses the DatoCMS webhook
   (webhookPayload.ts) and maps api_key+slug -> the affected URLs only
   (revalidationUrls.ts, ~12-20 for a book incl. its authors'/collection's
   pages) instead of re-fetching all ~670. Unknown models no-op; ?mode=full
   keeps the full sweep; removed the ineffective in-memory debounce.
2. ISR isr.expiration 7 -> 60 days (safety net only; freshness on-demand).
3. Lean card images: RESPONSIVE_IMAGE_CARD_FIELDS (no base64/srcSet) +
   srcSetCandidates={[1,2]} on card <Image>s (BookCard/AuthorCard/
   CollectionCard/Magazine/autori grids).
4. Paginate /libri 40/page: page 1 /libri, pages 2..N /libri/pagina/<n>;
   shared BooksCatalogSection + Pagination; sitemap + revalidation updated.
   BOOKS_PER_PAGE/buildBooksCataloguePaths in src/lib/books.ts.
5. Remove /llms-full.txt (866 KB, barely crawled) -> closes Security S4.

Local /libri: ~1.04 MB -> 321 KB (dev, unminified), 0 base64, 2-candidate
srcset. Build + astro check clean; webhook parser unit-tested (13 assertions).
Docs synced (decision-log 2026-06-20-fot-reduction, current-state, TODO,
list-*, guidelines). Per CLAUDE.md: no push.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
